**Board Change Announcement Summary:**  
- **Director Resignation & Appointment:** Karl Medak (representing major shareholder E8 Investments) resigns; replaced by Lew Starita (also from E8).  
- **Background:** Starita has 40+ years in ICT sector, prior Chair of RocketBoots pre-IPO.  
- **Reason:** Part of E8's planned 3-year transition.  

**No material impact on valuation, liquidity, or capital structure identified.**  

*(Omitted: Director accolades, operational background of RocketBoots.)*
